105	Black Myth: Wukong, jedna z nejočekávanějších her tohoto roku, dosáhla obrovského finančního úspěchu.	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"f8ykt\\"><b>I kdy\\u017e se hra Black Myth: Wukong zat\\u00edm nejv\\u00edce prosadila na \\u010d\\u00ednsk\\u00e9m trhu, celosv\\u011btov\\u00fd prodej p\\u0159ekro\\u010dil 18 milion\\u016f kopi\\u00ed a p\\u0159\\u00edjmy z prodeje na platform\\u011b Steam dosahuj\\u00ed t\\u00e9m\\u011b\\u0159 jedn\\u00e9 miliardy dolar\\u016f. </b></p><h2 data-block-key=\\"nl5s\\"><b>Black Myth: Wukong m\\u016f\\u017ee slavit</b></h2><p data-block-key=\\"9k0rk\\"><b>Black Myth: Wukong</b>, ak\\u010dn\\u00ed hra inspirovan\\u00e1 \\u010d\\u00ednsk\\u00fdmi m\\u00fdty a legendami, si od sv\\u00e9ho vyd\\u00e1n\\u00ed 20. srpna z\\u00edskala obrovskou pozornost, zejm\\u00e9na v \\u010c\\u00edn\\u011b. Podle nejnov\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00edch \\u00fadaj\\u016f od VG Insights tvo\\u0159\\u00ed hr\\u00e1\\u010di z \\u010c\\u00edny cel\\u00fdch 76 % z celkov\\u00e9 hr\\u00e1\\u010dsk\\u00e9 z\\u00e1kladny. </p><p data-block-key=\\"cing6\\">Navzdory tomu se <b>Black Myth: Wukong </b>m\\u016f\\u017ee pochlubit obrovsk\\u00fdm finan\\u010dn\\u00edm \\u00fasp\\u011bchem. Data z platformy Steam ukazuj\\u00ed, \\u017ee hra ji\\u017e p\\u0159ekro\\u010dila 880 milion\\u016f dolar\\u016f v hrub\\u00fdch p\\u0159\\u00edjmech, p\\u0159i\\u010dem\\u017e prodala v\\u00edce ne\\u017e 18 milion\\u016f kopi\\u00ed. Tato \\u010d\\u00edsla jsou o to p\\u016fsobiv\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00ed, \\u017ee hra je na trhu teprve necel\\u00e9 t\\u0159i t\\u00fddny. </p>", "id": "3cc48040-22ad-416a-b028-57c88d2252ea"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "b36c26a8-4dbf-427a-b33e-fed358804996"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"f8ykt\\">Na platform\\u011b <a linktype=\\"page\\" id=\\"81\\"><b>Steam</b></a> se hra nad\\u00e1le dr\\u017e\\u00ed mezi nejobl\\u00edben\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00edmi tituly. V dob\\u011b psan\\u00ed \\u010dl\\u00e1