e ne\\u017e 1 300 star\\u00fdch klasick\\u00fdch her z r\\u016fzn\\u00fdch hern\\u00edch syst\\u00e9m\\u016f 80. a 90. let 20. stolet\\u00ed. Najdete zde mnoho her ze star\\u00fdch syst\\u00e9m\\u016f <b>Atari, Nintendo</b> a dokonce i n\\u011bkolik titul\\u016f z p\\u016fvodn\\u00edho <b>PlayStationu 1</b>. V\\u0161echny tyto hry jsou uvedeny na ofici\\u00e1ln\\u00edch str\\u00e1nk\\u00e1ch aplikace. Krom\\u011b toho m\\u016f\\u017eete v t\\u011bchto hr\\u00e1ch plnit r\\u016fzn\\u00e9 mini v\\u00fdzvy, denn\\u00ed v\\u00fdzvy, a dokonce po\\u0159\\u00e1dat komunitn\\u00ed nebo sv\\u011btov\\u00e9 turnaje. Aplikace tak\\u00e9 podporuje r\\u016fzn\\u00e9 multiplayerov\\u00e9 funkce.</p><p data-block-key=\\"dh4h1\\">Je tu v\\u0161ak jeden men\\u0161\\u00ed probl\\u00e9m, kter\\u00fd by mohl n\\u011bkter\\u00e9 hr\\u00e1\\u010de odradit. Pro hran\\u00ed her na t\\u00e9to platform\\u011b je t\\u0159eba m\\u00edt zaplacen\\u00e9 p\\u0159edplatn\\u00e9, kter\\u00e9 stoj\\u00ed m\\u011bs\\u00ed\\u010dn\\u011b p\\u0159ibli\\u017en\\u011b <i>7 dolar\\u016f (159 K\\u010d) nebo ro\\u010dn\\u011b 39,99 dolar\\u016f (906 K\\u010d)</i>. A\\u010dkoli \\u010d\\u00e1stka nen\\u00ed p\\u0159\\u00edli\\u0161 vysok\\u00e1 vzhledem k tomu, co aplikace nab\\u00edz\\u00ed, bylo by p\\u0159\\u00ednosn\\u00e9, kdyby tv\\u016frci p\\u0159idali n\\u011bkolik titul\\u016f zdarma na vyzkou\\u0161en\\u00ed, zejm\\u00e9na pro hr\\u00e1\\u010de s pomalej\\u0161\\u00edm internetem.</p>", "id": "a220cd48-99d4-4186-aa76-f2c479fceb12"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<h3 data-block-key=\\"h72ag\\">Kde zat\\u00edm aplikace funguje a kde je\\u0161t\\u011b vyjde?</h3><p data-block-key=\\"bubf3\\">Pokud m\\u00e1te z\\u00e1jem a finance na vyzkou\\u0161en\\u00ed aplikace, m\\u016f\\u017eete si ji st\\u00e1hnout z ofici\\u00e1ln\\u00edch str\\u00e1nek nebo po\\u0159\\u00eddit na <b>Epic Games Store</b> pro PC \\u010di na sv\\u00e1 mobiln\\u00ed za\\u0159\\u00edzen\\u00ed (Android i iOS). Tv\\u016frci v\\u