00e1.</i></p><p data-block-key=\\"d8uu1\\">Jedno je ale jist\\u00e9 \\u2013 <b>Nintendo</b> se bude zuby nehty sna\\u017eit, aby soud s Pocketpair vyhr\\u00e1lo na pln\\u00e9 \\u010d\\u00e1\\u0159e.</p>", "id": "b6c09ea9-70f3-41e3-99c0-4731999c56e7"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<h3 data-block-key=\\"fdpw1\\">Vyd\\u00e1n\\u00ed hry mobily</h3><p data-block-key=\\"4c8rs\\">Navzdory tomuto sporu se studio rozhodlo zp\\u0159\\u00edstupnit hru je\\u0161t\\u011b \\u0161ir\\u0161\\u00edmu okruhu hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016f ne\\u017e d\\u0159\\u00edve. Po vyd\\u00e1n\\u00ed hry na platform\\u011b <a href=\\"https://superparmeni.eu/blog/palworld-oficialne-dorazil-na-ps5\\"><b>PlayStation</b></a> se v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159i zam\\u011b\\u0159ili na mobiln\\u00ed za\\u0159\\u00edzen\\u00ed. To by mo\\u017en\\u00e1 nebyla tak zaj\\u00edmav\\u00e1 zpr\\u00e1va, kdyby na v\\u00fdvoji portu nespolupracovalo zn\\u00e1m\\u00e9 studio Krafton, kter\\u00e9 stoj\\u00ed za otcem modern\\u00edch battle royale her, <b>PUBG</b>. </p><p data-block-key=\\"c8pv\\">Zn\\u00ed to opravdu zaj\\u00edmav\\u011b a jsme zv\\u011bdav\\u00ed, jak si s t\\u00edmto \\u00fakolem studio porad\\u00ed, proto\\u017ee u\\u017e maj\\u00ed ur\\u010dit\\u00e9 zku\\u0161enosti s v\\u00fdvojem her pro mobiln\\u00ed platformy.</p><embed embedtype=\\"media\\" url=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CxjZ13qz7Ys\\"/><p data-block-key=\\"d4abp\\"></p>", "id": "1a341cca-76ba-48d5-8f1e-850ca7372e35"}]	44	123	palworld, novinky, herní web	\N	0	2	0
