32364a"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "a4a7ed2d-ff82-4e8f-8857-612482ae3911"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"8oifk\\">P\\u0159esto\\u017ee <b>VRR</b> z\\u016fstane p\\u0159i spu\\u0161t\\u011bn\\u00ed beze zm\\u011bn, <b>PlayStation 5 Pro</b> p\\u0159in\\u00e1\\u0161\\u00ed v oblasti grafiky skute\\u010dn\\u011b ohromuj\\u00edc\\u00ed zlep\\u0161en\\u00ed, kter\\u00e9 je nejl\\u00e9pe vid\\u011bt na vlastn\\u00edch zku\\u0161enostech. <b>John Linnemann</b> si m\\u011bl mo\\u017enost zahr\\u00e1t na nov\\u00e9 konzoli b\\u011bhem <b>Tokyo Game Show</b> a popsal grafick\\u00e1 vylep\\u0161en\\u00ed jako<i> \\u201cgame-changing.\\u201d</i> Zvl\\u00e1\\u0161t\\u011b u titulu <b>Final Fantasy VII Rebirth</b> vylep\\u0161en\\u00ed <b>PSSR</b> (AI-powered upscaling) zp\\u016fsobilo, \\u017ee hra vypad\\u00e1 ost\\u0159e a \\u010dist\\u011b, ve <b>4K. </b> Dal\\u0161\\u00edm titulem, kter\\u00fd b\\u011b\\u017eel na <b>PlayStation 5 Pro</b> b\\u011bhem akce, byl <b>Gran Turismo 7</b>, kde byly rovn\\u011b\\u017e vid\\u011bt impozantn\\u00ed vylep\\u0161en\\u00ed. </p><p data-block-key=\\"1df35\\">Dal\\u0161\\u00ed informace o konzoli PlayStation 5 Pro naleznete pod p\\u0159ilo\\u017een\\u00fdm odkazem <a href=\\"https://superparmeni.eu/blog/playstation-5-pro-se-v-cesku-dostava-pres-zajimavou-cenovou-uroven\\"><b>ZDE</b></a>.</p><p data-block-key=\\"6n3oj\\"><b>T\\u011b\\u0161\\u00edte se na novou konzolie PlayStation 5 Pro? Dejte n\\u00e1m v\\u011bd\\u011bt n\\u00ed\\u017ee do koment\\u00e1\\u0159\\u016f. A nezapome\\u0148te se pod\\u00edvat tak\\u00e9 na na\\u0161e posledn\\u00ed video.</b></p><embed embedtype=\\"media\\" url=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CxjZ13qz7Ys\\"/><p data-block-key=\\"ndgi\\"></p>", "id": "fcb9edbc-8e18-4dbd-81fa-61ed19f7fcfc"}]	656	46	playstation 5, ps5 pro, sony, konzole	\N	0	0	0
